704807f-a.title: Brooklyn: Harway Avenue - Bay 43rd Street
704807f-a.text:
2625-2633 Harway Ave., east side, between Bay 43rd and 44th Streets,
showing in the foreground Hogan's roadhouse. The above numbers represent
the first two houses in this view.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
